The '''Supreme Serpent Master''', also known simply as the '''Supreme Master''', was the ruler of the [[Serpent Masters]] on [[Ophideraan]]. In [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]], the position was held by [[Tyrann]].

The Supreme Master ruled the Serpent Masters and their slaves from the upper levels of the [[Great Well]]. He wore a medallion around his neck that contained a transmitter used to control the [[Flying serpent|Ophideraan flying serpents]]. This was ultimately destroyed by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], and the Serpent Masters were overthrown by the slaves.

